name: Celestial Neighborhood
description:
A system of constellations, with each set generated by the owners of the piece! Collect to get your own randomly generated constellation. (Duplicates do not count, you can only have one constellation) by @rorscratch

Click the palette icon in the top right to change color palette
Click the music icon in the top left to toggle "music mode"
Click on a constellation to show the wallet/name that generated it, and if music mode is on play a randomly generated song.
